  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ いじち・こうすけ ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n旅順要塞司令官、参謀本部第一部長、第三軍参謀長、第11師団長、陸軍中将、妻雪子は<a href=\"../p/oiwao.html\">大山巌</a>の姪"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"01a.html\">一覧　（ア）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　鹿児島県出身。薩長土３藩からなる御親兵に選抜され上京。陸士２期卒。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　フランス、ドイツに留学し、近代法術を学ぶ。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　日露戦争に、<a href=\"../p/nmaresuk.html\">乃木希典司令官</a>の第三軍参謀長として従軍。旅順要塞攻略に携わる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1905/01ryojy.html\">旅順陥落</a>後、第三軍を離れ、旅順要塞司令官に就任。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
